<br>
Neutrals are somewhat rare, true ones that is.  If you're looking for RP, go evil.  There are a few great good-aligned RP guilds, but there are a ton of evil ones.  Just in general, you're a lot more likely to encounter casual RP from evils than goods.  Evils also seem to harbor less &quot;d00ds&quot;.  Elves are the d00d race on FV. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udracothesilent.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Draco the Silent</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/19/02 5:03:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm48.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=205.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hope you come to FV</span><hr size=1> Yes I was orginally thinking of going evil but I haven't made up my mind yet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 917<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/19/02 5:41:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm48.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=205.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmmm</span><hr size=1> Evils also seem more likely to declare a holy jihad upon you for being a false RP'er, too.  The definition of &quot;false&quot; seems to be somewhat vague.  IMHO, they're just looking for an excuse to /duel.<br>
