There's a stronger gnomish RP'ing community on this server than dwarvish or human, IMHO.  There's just too many humans of different types.  And the dwarves don't seem to have any racial cohesion at all.  So insofar as finding others of your race to help out and chat with, gnomes is a good bet (particularly if you want to be a dread gnome pirate or divorce lawyer ... see link in my sig).<br>
<br>
Now you should probably consider the times you play, and how you like to hunt ... if you don't hunt during US peak times, you'll need to be able to solo, so wizard or SK are probably the best bets.  If you like to always have a group, cleric... personally I found clerics dead boring to play, but they're always welcome, oh yes.  <br>
<br>
